    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can expend 1 point of mental focus to hide your appearance behind an illusion, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.oj36nfak6jc2s5ky]{Disguise Self}. The effect lasts for 1 minute per occultist level you possess.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, you can instead expend 2 points of mental focus to appear as a creature of a different type, but you must remain the same size.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, you can expend 1 additional point of mental focus to target a willing creature other than yourself with this ability.</p>"
